# RPG-TEAR

A tabletop RPG character sheet and management system.

## Overview

RPG-TEAR is designed to help players manage their character information, stats, and progression in an organized way.

## Features

- Character creation and management
- Stats tracking
- Inventory management
- Progress tracking

## Installation

1. Clone the repository
2. Follow setup instructions for your system
3. Configure your character sheet

## Usage

Open your character sheet file and start managing your RPG character.

